            <title>[CAMEL-2289] camel-bindy - csv - Make it easier to marshal with POJO out of the box</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-2289</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Its to ugly that you must use List&amp;lt;Map&amp;lt;String, Object&amp;gt;&amp;gt; to wrap you POJO to let Bindy be able to marhal my POJO to a CSV record.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be able to detect that its not a List but a plain POJO and construct the List itself and based on defaults.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
